## Typography Rules

**Always load these fonts on new pages:**
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

**Font assignment:**
- `var(--font-display)` = `"Bebas Neue"` → panel titles, dialog headers, section headers
- `var(--font-sans)` = `"Plus Jakarta Sans"` → all UI text (body, buttons, labels, nav)
- `var(--font-mono)` = `"DM Mono"` → code, hex values, numeric readouts

**Size scale — use ONLY these values:**
```
--font-size-xs:   11px   (labels, chips, uppercase tags)
--font-size-sm:   13px   (secondary UI)
--font-size-base: 14px   (default body)
--font-size-md:   15px   (emphasised body)
--font-size-lg:   18px   (section subtitles)
--font-size-xl:   22px   (panel/dialog titles)
```

**Uppercase label pattern:**
```css
font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.12em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--muted);
```

---

## Spacing Rules

**All spacing MUST be a multiple of 4px.** No exceptions.

```
4px  8px  12px  16px  24px  32px  48px  64px
```

**Common patterns:**
```css
--surface-pad: 14px;   /* Panel inner padding */
--surface-gap: 12px;   /* Between panels */
```

Never use: `5px, 6px, 7px, 9px, 10px, 11px, 13px, 15px, 17px, 18px, 19px, 21px, 22px, 23px, 25px`

> Exception: `10px` is acceptable ONLY for button padding (established pattern).

---

## Border Radius Rules

**Use only these values:**
```
4px   — tool indicators (square)
8px   — small elements
10px  — compact buttons
12px  — toolbar buttons, status chips
14px  — standard: buttons, inputs, chips (--radius-tight)
18px  — panels, control cards (--radius-card)
20px  — workflow pills, major panels (--radius-lg)
999px — full-round pills, eyebrow badges (--radius-full)
50%   — circular indicators
```

**Never use:** `6px, 16px, 24px, 30px, 50px` (not in scale)

---

## Component Patterns

### Button (standard)
```css
min-height: 44px;
padding: 10px 12px;
border-radius: 14px;
border: 1px solid var(--line);
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
color: var(--text);
font-family: var(--font-sans);
font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
font-weight: 600;
transition: background 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease,
            color 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
cursor: pointer;
```

Hover: `border-color: var(--line-strong); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); transform: translateY(-1px);`
Active: `border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(0,232,200,0.12);`
Disabled: `opacity: 0.45; cursor: not-allowed; pointer-events: none;`

### Input (standard)
```css
min-height: 44px;
padding: 10px 12px;
border-radius: 14px;
border: 1px solid var(--line);
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
color: var(--text);
font-family: var(--font-sans);
font-size: var(--font-size-base);
```

### Card / Panel
```css
padding: 14px;
border-radius: 18px;
border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
```

### Floating Panel (toolbar, inspector)
```css
border-radius: 16px;
border: 1px solid var(--line);
background: rgba(7,10,13,0.92);
backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
```

### Segmented Control Active State
```css
border-color: var(--accent);
background: rgba(0,232,200,0.12);
box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,232,200,0.08);
```

---

## Transition Rules

```css
--transition-fast: 120ms ease;   /* Hover reveals, icon states */
--transition-base: 200ms ease;   /* Default interactions */
```

- **Always** specify individual properties: `transition: background 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease`
- **Never** use `transition: all`
- **Never** exceed 300ms for UI interactions
- **Never** use spring/bounce easings — only `ease` or `ease-out`
- **Hover lift max:** `transform: translateY(-1px)`

---

## Animations

```css
@keyframes slideIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-4px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
/* animation: slideIn 120ms ease forwards; */
```

Only use for panel/inspector entrances. No page-level transitions, no character animations in UI.

---

## Focus States (Accessibility)

```css
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid rgba(0,232,200,0.35);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

All interactive elements must have visible `:focus-visible` styles.

---

## Shadow Rules

```css
--shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
--shadow-md: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.26);
--shadow-lg: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.38);
```

- Use `--shadow-sm` for cards, `--shadow-md` for floating panels, `--shadow-lg` for modals/toasts
- **Never** use colored shadows (except the cyan glow on active phase pills — see style guide §8.6)
- Inset highlight (top edge): `inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.045)`

