## Anti-Patterns (Forbidden)

| ❌ Never | ✅ Instead |
|---|---|
| `color: white` / `#fff` | `color: var(--text)` |
| `background: black` / `#000` | `background: var(--bg)` |
| `border-radius: 6px` | `var(--radius-sm)` (8px) |
| `gap: 10px` | `gap: 8px` or `gap: 12px` |
| `font-size: 16px` | `var(--font-size-base)` (14px) or `var(--font-size-lg)` (18px) |
| `transition: all 0.3s` | Explicit properties, 200ms |
| `font-family: Inter` | `var(--font-sans)` |
| Colored shadows | Black-only shadows |
| Light/white backgrounds | Dark backgrounds only |
| `transform: translateY(-3px)` on hover | Max `-1px` |
| Arbitrary spacing (5px, 7px, etc.) | 4px grid multiples |
| `font-weight: 900` | Max 800 |
